direction.raw_text: let's take a look. Mean Dude #4 takes the case and lays it flat in Azul's palms.
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: If it's a guitar like you say it is, we'll never bother you again... Mean Dude #4 unsnaps two of the latches, SNAP SNAP.
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: If it's not... He unsnaps three more... SNAP... SNAP... SNAP!
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: ... then we'll spray paint this street with your brains. He points the gun deep into Azul's face and cocks it. Azul closes his eyes. Mean Dude #5 lifts the lid. Azul hears a faint strumming sound, followed by the sound of the Mean Dude slamming the case shut. Azul opens his eyes. The Mean Dude resnaps the latches. SNAP... SNAP... SNAP-SNAP-SNAP!!!
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: (walking away) Sorry.... (CONTINUED)
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: . CONTINUED: They walk away leaving Azul wondering what happened. INT. AMADEUS - DAY Domino, Mariachi, and Assistant are standing at the bar.
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: Look, as long as you don't carry the case around, they'll leave you alone. It's that guy they're after.
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: (putting on his coat) I better put this upstairs... He grabs the case and begins to take it to the stairs, but he pauses for it feels different to him. He slowly looks down at it. EXT. STREET - DAY Azul watches the Mean Dudes go and when tey turn the corner he puts the case on the ground to open it. EXT. AROUND THE CORNER - DAY The Mean Dudes are rounding the corner, but Mean Dude #5, who is last, snaps his fingers and motions to the others to keep quiet and to watch Azul INT. AMADEUS - DAY Mariachi shakes the case, and puts it on the counter as if to open it... but he doesn't need to check it. He knows it's not his guitar.
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: What's wrong? Mariachi looks at her startled, then runs out of the bar with the case. EXT. AROUND THE CORNER - DAY Mean Dudes are watching Azul unsnap his case. EXT. STREET - DAY Azul opens the lid, revealing Mariachi's guitar.
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: . EXT. AROUND THE CORNER - DAY MEAN DUDE #5 That's him... The Mean Dudes start walking towards Azul as the camera tracks back with them. Azul slams the case shut, wondering what the hell is going on. He looks up and notices the Mean Dudes walking towards him. He stands up and slowly walks in the other direction. EXT. A BLOCK AWAY - DAY Mariachi is running through the streets and onto the sidewalk. EXT. STREET - DAY The bad guys are pulling out their weapons. Mariachi bolts around the corner. Now everyone is on the same sidewalk. Mariachi and Azul are on each end of the street with the Mean Dudes in between them. Azul turns and sees Mariachi with his guitar case. Mean Dude #5 turns and sees Mariachi, too.
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: That's him... The two other Mean Dudes exchange glances. Mean Dude #5 stalks after Mariachi, so the other two follow. Mariachi looks to Azul for help. Azul tips the imaginary hat to Mariachi and walks away. EXT. ANOTHER STREET - DAY Mariachi runs through the street almost getting hit. Bullets are flying as the Mean Dudes are firing at him as they run. EXT. DEAD END - DAY Mariachi leaps up over a few cars and ends up in a dead end. He turns around, drops the case on the ground and opens it. A million weapons seem to stare back at him when he opens it. He is frantic. He grabs a small gun, shakes it in his hand, doesn't like the feel. He tosses it back in. EXT. STREET - DAY The Mean Dudes are barreling down the street. One turns towards the dead end.
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: . EXT. DEAD END - DAY Mariachi pulls out the MAC-10 and blasts the first Mean Dude he sees. He grabs the case and runs out into the street, jumping onto a truck and blasting the other Mean Dude from up there. He sees Mean Dude #5 run away. Mariachi comes off the truck and walks through the streets in slow motion. Peolple are staring at him as if he was Azul the killer. Mariachi walks straight to the bar. A BOY is bouncing a ball on one of the sidewalks. INT. AZUL'S HIDEOUT - DAY The camera dollies past the vacant pool table, and over to a Rat sitting in a chair, drinking a beer. The other Rat is pacing back and forth in front of the sitting Rat. Azul enters the room. Throwing his guitar case onto the pool table as a grand entrance gesture. The sitting Rat stands beside the pacing Rat.
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: I'm sorry we left...
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: ... We didn't know what to do...
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: ... We figured you could defend yourself!!! Rat #2 nods in agreement. Azul unsnaps one of the latches. SNAP!
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: You thought I could defend myself... SNAP! SNAP!
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: ... against three armed men... SNAP!
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: ... using this? He opens the case and the guitar sparkles at them. The Rats exchange glances. They look at the guitar then back at Azul.
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: My case got switched with some maricon mariachi! (CONTINUED)
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: . CONTINUED:
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: Where is this mariachi?
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: He's dead by now... So, I want you to go look for my case. The two Rats are about to leave.
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: Leave me a weapon. Both Rats take out their guns. Azul takes Rat #2's gun.
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: That was disloyal of you to leave me out there. You should be as loyal to me as you are to each other. The Rats exchange glances, then aim their eyes back to the floor. Azul turns to Rat #2.
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: Are you loyal?
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: (after glancing at Rat #1) Yes.
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: (to Rat #1) Are you loyal?
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: Yes. Azul gestures to Rat #2.
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: Then shoot him. Rat #1 turns to Rat #2 who is in shock.
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: You are loyal, are you not? SHOOT HIM. Or I shoot you. Azul aims his gun at Rat #1, who immediately aims his gun at Rat #2. Rat #2 is sweating bullets. Rat #1 puts his gun down.
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: I can't. (CONTINUED)
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: . CONTINUED: (2)
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: Why not?
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: You said we should be as loyal to you as we are to each other. I couldn't shoot him, for that would be as disloyal as shooting you. Rat #2 glances back and forth between Rat #1 and Azul.
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: Very good. Now go find my case. Azul puts his gun down and motions the rats to leave. They leave. When they exit, Rat #1 turns to Rat #2 and snaps his fingers. Rat #2 shakes his hand. They leave. INT. DOMINO'S LOFT - NIGHT Domino is dabbing hydrogen peroxide onto a cotton swab. She applies it to Mariachi's body scars on his back. Mariachi has his eyes closed. He washes the blood from his face.
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: Where were you when he came into the bar?
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: I was on the phone, talking to a friend that knows what's going on.
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: Did you mention me?
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: No... He told me the man in black is Azul.
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: If his name is Azul, why doesn't he wear blue?
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: I don't know... Anyway, he's killing the men of the town drug dealer. The dealer's name is Mauricio. But he's known as Moco.
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: And Moco is sending these men to find Azul. So, why do they chase me? (CONTINUED)
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: . CONTINUED:
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: They have never seen Azul... only Moco knows him. My friend says the description Moco gave his men was that he wears black, and carries a guitar case. Sounds like you, no?
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: Couldn't you tell your friend that there are two people like that in his town? One is a killer, and one is a mariachi.
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: Only special people can talk to Moco. Besides, you've killed a few of his men, now. Your best option is to keep out of sight, stop wearing black, and to hide that stupid case until this is all over. EXT. MOCO'S RANCH - DAY Mean Dude #5 comes in and approaches Moco.
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: He got away... but I got a good look at him. Moco takes out a cigarette and puts it in his mouth.
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: Coca, Caca, Beto were killed. Moco takes out a match.
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: He won't get away again, Moco. I promise. Moco lights his match across Mean Dude #5's face and lights his cigarette. Mean Dude #5 walks away, as Moco flicks his match at him in slow motion. INT. DOMINO'S LOFT - NIGHT Mariachi is about to lay on the floor. She tosses him a blanket.
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: Are you always closed Monday nights, or did you close since I can't play my guitar tonight? (CONTINUED)
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: . CONTINUED:
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: Mondays are my day off. Want to play a game?
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: Sure. The phone rings. Domino gets up to answer it. Mariachi reaches under his blanket for a small mirror and combs his hair, putting spit in his hair to slick it down. He quickly stashes the mirror.
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: (into phone) Hello?
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: (into phone) Come see me.
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: (into phone) I can't.
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: (into phone) Please. Moco is sitting at a table playing cards.
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: (into phone) I don't feel well. I've got to go.
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: (into phone) Have you ridden the bike?
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: (into phone) No... I've got to go... She hangs up.
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: Boyfriend.
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: (quiet as if thinking) No... (CONTINUED)
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: . CONTINUED: (2)
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: I can't figure out something. You tell me you're poor. Poor family. Yet you've got this place.
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: (sighing) This place is a gift.
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: From who?
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: From Mauricio.
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: From Mauricio? The man trying to kill me?
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: He's not trying to kill you, his man had you confused with Azul.
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: Same thing.
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: Look, you now how if you want to impress a girl, you send her flowers, candy, jewelry until you win her love?
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: Yes.
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: If one present doesn't work, you keep sending bigger and better things until you win her or you're broke?
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: Correct...
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: Well, Mauricio sent me flowers, then jewelry, then he gave me a job at his saloon, then he gave me the whole saloon... etc.
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: He's still giving you things?
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: He'll never run out of money. (CONTINUED)
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: . CONTINUED: (3)
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: And you accept it all? What's the last thing he sent you? Domino walks over to the counter and picks up a key.
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: A motorcycle. Mariachi laughs.
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: He wants me to ride out to his ranch when I've decided to be his. He thinks he's close to having me.
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: Is he?
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: (pause) He was. She sits next to Mariachi.
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: Not anymore. They kiss. She gets up and is about to turn off the lights.
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: So, you really are from a poor family. CLICK!
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: (in the dark) I remember when I was growing up, we were so poor, that my brothers and sisters and I all slept on the same blanket stretched out across the floor. We had to sleep in a circle, with our fingers in each other's ears, to keep the bugs from crawling into them.
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: (after a pause) Ay, wey... Domino laughs.
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: . INT. AMADEUS - DAY Domino hands Mariachi a wad of money. Mariachi sees the money and looks up at her bewildered.
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: Here's a little bit I've saved. I want you to go get a new guitar. Mariachi starts to put up his hand as if to refuse it.
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: Take it, stupid. I'm not saying go by the best one, just a temporary one so you can play again tonight. Mariachi stops and thinks... He looks up at her questioningly, then he shrugs an "OK" and grabs the money and jogs out excitedly. Domino is smiling. EXT. STREET - DAY Mariachi walks down the sidewalk, passing curioso shops. The camera is low and zoomed in all the way. Mariachi stops by one of the window that has a guitar in the glass. He pulls his money and counts it. He stops after he notices someone's reflection in the window. He turns around and sees it is Mean Dude #5 right across the street. He meets up with another Mean Dude. They are standing right behind Mariachi. Mariachi is pretending to still look at the window. The Mean Dudes walk past Mariachi so Mariachi walks in the opposite direction. Mean Dude #5 stops and then turns around slowly. Far zoomed shot of Mariachi walking down the street with guys behind him. They start after him.
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: That's him... Tracking shot following Mariachi. Tracking shot in front of Mean Dudes walking at Mariachi. Mean Dude #5 pulls out a small walkie-talkie and calls his buddy in the truck a block away.
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: (into walkie-talkie) Loco, he's headed your way... black pants, white shirt.
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: . IN A TRUCK DOWN THE STREET LOCO starts the truck and starts driving slowly across the street. As he turns on the corner, Mariachi sees the truck and casually climbs inside and hides in the back. Mean Dude #5 turns the corner when whispers into walkie-talkie.
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: (into walkie-talkie) Where did he go, Loco?
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: (laughs, into walkie-talkie) He got in my truck. Mean Dude #5 laughs.
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: (into walkie-talkie) Take him around the block. Mean Dude #5 taps his buddy and they start running down the block. Mariachi is in back the truck searching for a weapon. The truck stops. Mariachi rolls to the side and gently lifts his head. POV Mariachi sees the two Mean Dudes walking at him. Mariachi turns and Loco is there to knock him in the face with the rifle butt. Mariachi falls into truck, blood trickling from his dizzying head. He tries to get up a bit, but Loco is in the truck now, and slams the rifle down into his face hard... Blackout. DUSTY ROAD TO MOCO'S Mariachi is unconcious in the back of Loco's truck. Mean Dude #5 and other Mean Dudes are riding in back with Mariachi. EXT. ROAD TO MOCO'S - DAY The above scene intercuts back and forth with the arrival of Loco. Loco arrives at the gate, Mean Dude #5 opens the gate, they drive through. The truck is facing Moco so he can't see Mariachi yet. Mean Dude #5 closes the gate and walks over to the truck, opens the back door, and calls Moco over. Moco walks over to the truck and looks inside.
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: . EXT. TRUCK - DAY Mariachi is laying there unconcious, Moco puts his arm around Mean Dude #5, who is looking very proud, and Moco pulls out a cigarette and a match.
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: That's not him. Moco strikes the match behind Mean Dude #5's head. Mean Dude #5 stops smiling. INT. AMADEUS - DAY Domino is waiting on customers. She glances at her watch. A few seconds later she glances at it again. She looks very worried. INT. AZUL'S HIDEOUT - DAY Azul's Rats burst into the hideout. FOUR GIRLS pop up over the partition with guns. The Rats stop in their tracks. The girls sigh a "oh, it's them" sigh and slink back to bed. Top shot of them trying to wake Azul. Azul wakes up and looks over the partition.
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: Where's my case?
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: We couldn't find it.
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: We heard they caught you and were taking you to Moco's ranch.
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: ... so we came to see if it was true. Azul thinks a moment. He stands up.
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: They caught the mariachi. Azul dresses, smiling... INT. MOCO'S RANCH - DAY Mariachi is in a holding cell at the ranch. He twitches, finally waking up. He sees a GUARD outside and finds a way to escape. (CONTINUED)
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: . CONTINUED: He grabs the guard's assault rifle and turns a corner. Two men grab him. He slams the butt of the rifle, knocking the wind and teeth out of BAD GUY #1, then he kicks down and breaks the shin bone of BAD GUY #2 who screams out in agony. Mariachi silences him by karate punching his throat. The Bad Guy gurgles and hits the ground. Angle from the ground as Mariachi smashes the guy with is gun. He crawls up a wall, trying to escape as quietly as he can. He sees TWO MORE MEN running towards him since they heard some noise. Mariachi aims his assault rifle at the blue Chevy parked behind him. He fires and it explodes. Mariachi jumps Loco, gets him to drive him to the saloon. He also takes Loco's money. EXT. BOYSTOWN SALOON - DAY Azul walks into frame, looks around then proceeds into the bar. INT. AMADEUS - DAY Azul goes inside and finds Domino tending the bar.
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: What can I get you?
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: One beer. She grabs a bottle and slams it down on the counter unopened. He eyes her admirably and then pops the top with one hand. He guzzles the drink, slamming it down empty.
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: Anything else?
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: (nodding) My guitar case.
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: Where's Mariachi?
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: Where's my case?
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: Upstairs. (CONTINUED)
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: . CONTINUED:
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: Get it. Domino grabs another beer for him and runs to get the case. (In between this time, Mariachi escapes with Loco.) She returns, slamming it to the floor.
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: If you want your mariachi back, come with me.
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: Why will you help me?
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: Because you know where Moco's ranch is... I don't. Domino calls her Assistant.
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: You help me, I'll help you.
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: Let's go. They leave. The Assistant tends to the bar. ROAD TO MOCO'S They drive out to Moco's ranch in Azul's truck. Little do they know, they passed Loco's truck with Mariachi crouched in the passenger seat. He gets up after the truck passes. Mariachi didn't know it was Domino in Azul's truck or he could have turned around and kept her from going to Moco's ranch. They arrive at the gate and het out of the truck.
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: (over the gate) Mauricio!! Azul grabs Domino and points a gun to her head. He whispers to her...
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: Play along... He kicks at the gate. (CONTINUED)
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: . CONTINUED:
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: Open the gate or she's dead! The gate opens and we see Moco standing at a three-quarter stance, flanked with his men on both sides. Azul drags Domino in and faces her at Moco with a gun to her head.
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: (to Domino) I'm sorry he used you to get to me, Domino. Azul cocks the pistol.
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: Azul, let her go and you'll get your money.
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: Moco, give me my money or I ruin your clothes with her blood. Moco signals his men to get the money.
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: What have you done with Mariachi?
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: Who?
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: The musician your men confused with Azul.
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: (staring at her) So that's why you were busy that night... Azul is glancing between Domino and Moco.
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: ... you had that little monkey climbing all over you.
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: Give me my money or I kill her NOW!!!
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: After all I've done for you, this is how you treat me?
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: I never asked you for anything until now. Let Mariachi go. (CONTINUED)
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: . CONTINUED: (2) Azul is anxious now.
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: I swear I'll kill her!
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: No you won't. I will. Moco pulls out his gun and shoots her in the heart. She falls limp in Azul's arms. Azul tries hold her up, but she's dead. Azul rests her on the ground, looking down at her, wondering why it's all come to this.
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: All I wanted was my rightful share. But you've got to kill everybody.
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: You feel sorry for her, don't you? See, that's why you can't ever be as big as me. Azul slowly looks at Moco.
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: (aiming gun) Because you have too much heart. Moco shoots Azul in the heart. Azul had his hands to his side, and now he falls to his knees. Moco shoots him again, and Azul dies next to Domino. Mean Dude #5 is exchanging glances with the others. No one seems to be on Moco's side. EXT. NEAR SALOON - DAY Mariachi is still in Loco's truck.
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: Stop here. Loco stops the truck and Mariachi gets out. Loco drives back when Mariachi motions for him to leave. Mariachi watches him go then dashes around the corner to the saloon. INT. AMADEUS - DAY Mariachi runs into the bar...
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: Domino!!! We're leaving!!! Right now!!! (CONTINUED)
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: . CONTINUED: The Assistant rushes over to Mariachi.
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: She's gone.
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: Where is she?
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: Looking for you. Mariachi is about to race upstairs.
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: She gave the case back to that guy. She left with him to find you. Mariachi tries to make sense of it all for a minute before grabbing the gun from under the counter and rushing upstairs. INT. DOMINO'S LOFT - DAY Mariachi grabs the key to the motorcycle and runs out. The motorcycle burns down the road. MARIACHI ON THE ROAD TO MOCO'S Mariachi barrels down the road on the motorcycle. EXT. MOCO'S RANCH - DAY Moco is walking away from the bodies.
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: Bring that musician out here so he can be reunited with my Domino. Some men go to check. Cut back and forth with Mariachi coming.
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: He's gone, sir.
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: Find him!! Mariachi rides through the semi-open gate... stopping at the bodies. He dismounts the bike and holds Domino. He has the gun in the back of his pants. You can see it while his back is to the camera and men are approaching him. Moco comes for the show. (CONTINUED)
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: . CONTINUED:
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: (good shot) So you're the little mariachi that came to town, killed my men, and stole my girl... Mariachi slowly lifts his eyes to Moco.
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: You are very talented. Mariachi stands, hands up.
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: I bet you play the guitarra real well, huh? Mariachi says nothing.
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: (raising gun) Not anymore. Moco fires into Mariachi's left hand. Mariachi grimaces, crumbling to the floor. He keeps a tight grip on his hand. When he opens his hand to see the damage, the camera can see right through his hand for a reverse shot of his face through the hole.
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: Now get the hell off my property and take your hand with you!!! Moco is laughing and looking at his men for support, but no one else laughs. Mariachi tries to stand, but he falls back. When he rises again he has the gun in his hand. He shoots Moco in the chest. Moco falls back and hits the ground hard. He gasps for air... Moco's men gather around him. Mean Dude #5 crouches down to check Moco's throat pulse. Moco's dead. Mean Dude #5 strikes a match across Moco's face and lights up a cigarette. He turns and walks away. The others follow. Mariachi wraps a tourniquet on his arm, kisses Domino, opens Azul's case, sees the weapons, and rides off with it. MARIACHI ON THE ROAD He looks back at the town behind him, then places his hand on the motorcycle to drive off. We notice the metal brace on his hand. (CONTINUED)
direction.name: direction
